You are The Moon

Hope, expectation, Bright promises.

The Moon is a card of magic and mystery - when prominent you know that nothing is as it seems, particularly when it concerns relationships. All logic is thrown out the window.

The Moon is all about visions and illusions, madness, genius and poetry. This is a card that has to do with sleep, and so with both dreams and nightmares. It is a scary card in that it warns that there might be hidden enemies, tricks and falsehoods. But it should also be remembered that this is a card of great creativity, of powerful magic, primal feelings and intuition. You may be going through a time of emotional and mental trial; if you have any past mental problems, you must be vigilant in taking your medication but avoid drugs or alcohol, as abuse of either will cause them irreparable damage. This time however, can also result in great creativity, psychic powers, visions and insight. You can and should trust your intuition.

Ok, so... a dear friend of mine, suggested I should refresh this journal...well, I suppose he's right... there's no aim in keeping an lj and not refreshing it! So, I think i would take this occasion to remind one of the greatest tragedies my city has ever lived : the flood of 1966. Firenze lived moments of real terror; fear ruled the city, nobody knew what would have happened in the following hours, because there were no certainties at all. But since for every drop of rain there's always a rain of sushine, perhaps an angel remembered all those marvellous florentin artists who contributed to elevate his myth all over the world, and lended a hand to this ripped city, leading a bunch of wholeharted people come from the farthest places on earth to help Florence to rise up again. These generous, brave men and women, have always been remembered as "The angel of mud"... and we have to thank them for every book, masterpiece and sparkle of beauty Florence can be proud of. I'm young, and I haven't lived those dark days...

Oh, Lord...It's been a long time since my last post...I'm lazy, as you probably noticed...well, yesterday, I made a photo of my dear Titta, my aunt's dog...she's incredibly sweet..and she has a sad background :my aunt found her in an old cage, where a heartless man used to keep her, because she was not good enough for hunting... well, my aunt practically "kidnapped" her!! And now she lives happily with a woman that takes care of her...

Thanks to the wonderful marita...
You Are 30% Boyish and 70% Girlish
Even if you're not a girl, you're very feminine. You're in touch with your feelings, and your heart rules you. A bit of a emotional roller coaster, one moment you're up and the next you're down. But no matter what, you try to be as cute and perky as possible.
How Boyish or Girlish Are You?

Ten Top Trivia Tips about Morgana!

  1. The International Space Station weighs about 500 tons and is the same size as Morgana.
  2. All gondolas in Venice must be painted black unless they belong to Morgana.
  3. Never store Morgana at room temperature.
  4. Fifty-two percent of Americans drink Morgana!
  5. Some hotels in Las Vegas have Morgana floating in their swimming pools!
  6. If you lick Morgana ten times, you will consume one calorie!
  7. Morgana can turn her stomach inside out.
  8. More people are killed by Morgana each year than die in aeroplane accidents!
  9. It is impossible to fold Morgana more than seven times.
  10. The first Morgana was made in 1853, and had no pedals.
